cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper deals with social relationship understanding, which involves natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel structured knowledge graph and a deep neural network architecture, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.AI and cs.LG (Learning) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of contextual information, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper mentions the use of image data, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
